name: Azar
description:
Risografia scanned, 3 colors. 

This work was done in 2020, at the height of the pandemic. Is bad luck a strong word, stamps the environment as a celebration, or would it be an outburst? Around bad luck, symbols with the purpose of guarding, protecting and saluting. In rue corners close the circle, bad luck has passed, 2020 too. It's history now.
